# `psql` short codes

    \?             display help
    \q             quit psql
    \c DBNAME      connect to database DBNAME (can be URL)
    \conninfo      display information about current connection
    \l             list databases
    \d             list tables, sequences, ...
    \d+            list with additional info
    \d NAME        describe table, sequence, ...
    \i FILE        execute commands from FILE
    \o FILE        send all query results to FILE
    \e             edit last command in $EDITOR
    \e FILE        edit file in editor; contents are copied into query buffer
    \du            show user accounts
    \timing        toggle timing of commands



